executionArgs.additionalInstruction: Test the Wine Club SaaS Platform frontend including admin dashboard with real-time metrics, member management with Square sync, plan management with Square customer groups, club setup wizard with credential persistence, customer preferences and custom shipments, fulfillment workflow with CSV export/upload, embeddable signup widget with real data only, SaaS admin portal for multi-club management, and authentication flows with multi-tenant data isolation. Focus on verifying no fallback/dummy data is displayed and all Square API integrations work correctly.
